HEADWORD: Blackwater State
<hw>Black"wa`ter State</hw>. <def>Nebraska; -- a nickname alluding to
the dark color of the water of its rivers, due to the presence of a
black vegetable mold in the soil.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

